name: Steampunk Mechanical Pocket Watch Necklace
description:
This gorgeous, real-working, timepiece is perfect for the lover of anything steampunk.

This mechanical pocket watch pendant with real-working, visible moving cogs, has a diameter of about 1.75 inches and weighs 78 grams. 

Featured on a long, 30 inch, matching, brass colored chain.

Along with this order you will also receive a print out on how the watch works and how the time can be adjusted.

**This item will take at least a week to ship out.

name: Hermione Granger's Time Turner Necklace
description:
"I mark the hours, every one, Nor have I yet outrun the Sun. My use and value, unto you, Are gauged by what you have to do."

PRE-ORDER**

A replica of Hermione Granger's time turner necklace from 'Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban'. A beautiful piece which can be worn to show your love of the beautiful, yet highly intelligent, witch.

Each time turner is featured on a matching chain measuring around 20 inches.

**This is a pre-order and will be shipped out the first week (or the second depending on the amount of orders) of January!

name: Bullet Shell Quartz Points
description:
At only $22, this item is a steal! Seen on other sites for upwards of $60! However, this is only the special release price and the cost will rise before you know it!

.38mm brass bullet shells surround a single semi-precious quartz point of varying colors. 

The bullet shell alone is approximately 1.25" and due to the fact that each stone is natural, the size for them vary.

Each bullet shell pendant will arrive on a long, 30" gold colored chain.

Note: Every stone is unique, therefore the stones you receive on your necklace will differ slightly from those in the pictures.

Each stone pendant is hand selected for their color and shape so only the best quality gems are used in making out jewelry.

Handmade with love.
